  "texts": [
    "This follows from the fact that AI optimizes for its goal.",
    "This condition is fulfilled if and only if (1) the AI believes it is capable of achieving the instrumental goal, (2) the AI believes that achieving the instrumental goal would be useful and (3) the expected costs of pursuing the instrumental goal are relatively low.",
    "Since AI capable of disempowering humanity would be very smart, (1) and (2) should be fulfilled with respect to the instrumental goal of disempowering humanity.",
    "Disempowering humanity would be very useful for a wide range of goals, since it rules out a likely source of interference with its goals and provides access to enormous resources.",
    "Thus, it has high expected benefits."
  ],
